title: Matt McCusker: Prince of Trash
description: Comedian and Podcaster Matt McCusker joins us this week. Matt talks about his WILD childhood growing up outside of Philly, his family owning a trash company, and drinking milk for dinner. You know Matt from hosting Matt & Shane's Secret Podcast. PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/AreYouGarbage Follow Kevin: https://www.instagram.com/kevinryancomedy/ Follow Foley: https://www.instagram.com/foleygrams/ Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the the test. Steal shampoo from hotels? Own a George Forman Grill? Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
